      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute gem of a car. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been totally pampered and kept in pristine shape. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new and runs like a dream, this is definitely the one! I've taken such good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a home where it'll be just as appreciated. It\u2019s a real head-turner, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
