    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies. It maintains factory tolerances with a pristine undercarriage and zero subframe fatigue. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers lightning-fast shifts, paired with an active M differential for optimal torque vectoring. Finished in Interlagos Blue over Novillo leather, the cabin exhibits zero bolster wear. Meticulously serviced with documented rod bearing prophylaxis and recent throttle actuator replacement. This is a turn-key, showroom-quality example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
