      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality masterpiece. Having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior is equally immaculate, featuring supple, unscuffed leather that still carries a fresh scent, with every switch and electronic feature operating with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to display, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records demonstrating that every maintenance milestone was met early. It rides on a fresh set of premium tires and delivers a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and indistinguishable from new. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
